    "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in frenetic water balloon battles in <strong>Don Pepe y sus globos</strong>, an arena fighter for up to 4 players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/a4539e0cca665c008c3899a3b762f789.avif?t=1761655513\" width=616 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, Don Pepe had an idea to make a quick buck: sell water balloons to his neighborhood's kids. What started as a simple game ended up turning into a legitimate sport where competitors square up to throw water balloons at each other with only one of them prevailing: the last one that's still dry. Can you be the champion?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/21b0521508141c0a67803cb75757f6cf.avif?t=1761655513\" width=616 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/f6d9c9aad3bc6b492088c396f573b36e.poster.avif?t=1761655513\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/f6d9c9aad3bc6b492088c396f573b36e.webm?t=1761655513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/f6d9c9aad3bc6b492088c396f573b36e.mp4?t=1761655513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw water balloons at your rivals to soak them! The last one standing wins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your arrow shows the opponent you will throw your balloons at.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill balloons at the reload areas to continue fighting. You can't attack while you're reloading, but you can be attacked.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll and run to avoid attacks, but if you run out of energy you'll be vulnerable.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/c381029815b5f3ceadc5bd9338e6e30d.avif?t=1761655513\" width=616 height=114 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense water balloon battles with easy to learn gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many characters and stages to fight in</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different game mods including casual, tournament, league, and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with your friends both locally and online!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/5a1273f2ad51defc2cf67e749b7941ca.avif?t=1761655513\" width=616 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The most recent demo (v0.5) includes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 playable charactes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battles for up to 4 players and/or bots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casual game mode: free for all</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only local play (no online)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/1fcbf6c97e28e4fb873fa624f9a6e294.avif?t=1761655513\" width=800 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original prototype developed during<strong> Global Game Jam 2024.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valdivia, Chile</p>",
    "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in frenetic water balloon battles in <strong>Don Pepe y sus globos</strong>, an arena fighter for up to 4 players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/a4539e0cca665c008c3899a3b762f789.avif?t=1761655513\" width=616 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, Don Pepe had an idea to make a quick buck: sell water balloons to his neighborhood's kids. What started as a simple game ended up turning into a legitimate sport where competitors square up to throw water balloons at each other with only one of them prevailing: the last one that's still dry. Can you be the champion?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/21b0521508141c0a67803cb75757f6cf.avif?t=1761655513\" width=616 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/f6d9c9aad3bc6b492088c396f573b36e.poster.avif?t=1761655513\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/f6d9c9aad3bc6b492088c396f573b36e.webm?t=1761655513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/f6d9c9aad3bc6b492088c396f573b36e.mp4?t=1761655513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw water balloons at your rivals to soak them! The last one standing wins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your arrow shows the opponent you will throw your balloons at.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill balloons at the reload areas to continue fighting. You can't attack while you're reloading, but you can be attacked.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll and run to avoid attacks, but if you run out of energy you'll be vulnerable.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/c381029815b5f3ceadc5bd9338e6e30d.avif?t=1761655513\" width=616 height=114 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense water balloon battles with easy to learn gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many characters and stages to fight in</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different game mods including casual, tournament, league, and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with your friends both locally and online!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/5a1273f2ad51defc2cf67e749b7941ca.avif?t=1761655513\" width=616 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The most recent demo (v0.5) includes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 playable charactes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battles for up to 4 players and/or bots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casual game mode: free for all</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only local play (no online)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4079810/extras/1fcbf6c97e28e4fb873fa624f9a6e294.avif?t=1761655513\" width=800 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original prototype developed during<strong> Global Game Jam 2024.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valdivia, Chile</p>",
